{{Infobox person |name = Rajinder Johar |image = |image_size = 350px |caption = Dr. Rajinder Johar at [[NGO]] in December 2014. | birth_date = 19 January 1948 | birth_place = [[Jalandhar]], [[Punjab (India)|Punjab, India]] |nationality = [[India]]n |organization=Family of Disabled |alma_mater = |known for= Family of Disabled (FOD) |occupation = Social Service |awards = [[public welfare]] |footnotes = |website= [http://www.familyofdisable.org/ familyofdisable.org/] }} '''Rajinder Johar''' is a quadriplegic philanthropist who runs an NGO by the name Family of Disabled (FoD)<ref>[http://www.thehindu.com/features/metroplus/society/niche-news/article4541955.ece Article on Dr Rajinder Johar ] Article on Dr Rajinder Johar in The Hindu News.</ref> which looks after the betterment of disabled persons in Delhi in more ways than one. As a result of a bullet injury in 1986 in an attempted robbery in his house, Johar was left paralyzed and bedridden.<ref>[http://gulfnews.com/life-style/people/rajinder-johar-s-story-1.25742 Life Story of Dr Rajinder Johar ] Life Story of Dr Rajinder Johar.</ref> After six years of depressions, he decided to help the disabled become self-sufficient and thus founded the Family of Disabled. Johar's service of the disabled over two decades has won him several awards and accolades.<ref>[http://www.outlookindia.com/article/Quadriplegic-Rajinder-Johar-Lends-Hope-To-The-Disabled/206381 Rajinder Johar Lends Hope To The Disabled ] Rajinder Johar Lends Hope To The Disabled</ref>
Family of Disabled (FOD) was founded in 1992 by Johar, himself a quadriplegic who has been bedridden for the last 22 years.<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wbxE9X_T3hk Dr Rajinder Johar at Lok Sabha TV] Video of Dr Rajinder Johar at Lok Sabha TV.</ref> Based in New Delhi, FOD’s mission is to build and nurture the capacities of persons<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vOzIXuS3rtA Dr Rajinder Johar at NDTV] Video of Dr Rajinder Johar at ND TV.</ref> with disabilities through different sustainable interventions for improving their quality of life,<ref>[http://ibnlive.in.com/news/a-complete-users-guide-to-aamir-khans-satyamev-jayate/275552-7.html Satyamev Jayate Show] [[Satyamev Jayate (TV series)|Satyamev Jayate]].</ref> making them self-reliant and facilitating their mainstreaming
